# Decision-Driven Automation Lab

## Problem
Most automation is reactive and disconnected from real observability.

## Solution
A decision-driven pipeline using:
- Prometheus (metrics)
- Python agent (decision layer)
- Ansible (execution)

## Architecture
metrics → Prometheus → agent → Ansible

## How to run
1. start metrics server
2. start docker
3. run agent

## Demo
- CPU normal → no action
- CPU high → remediation triggered
